%
% (a) |y' = y tan t + sin t, y(0) = -1/2| from |t = 0| to |t = pi|
%
% (b) |y' = 1 / y^2 , y(1) = 1| from |t=1| to |t=10|
%
% (c) |y' =  1 - t y / 2, y(0) = -1| from |t=0| to |t=10|
